name: Issue-tracker
body:
### Welcome to our issue tracker GitHub page.
The aim of this project is to provide basic funcionality of issue tracker. During the making process we'd like to learn how to create web based Java applications using available new techniques.

### How to build this project
You can build it using Gradle. Enter the directory with the project and type:

```
$ gradle build
```

### Authors and Contributors
Our team consists of three contributors: @agjanowicz, @kokoss, @Thurs997.
